                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "5788204"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "2.2. Percentages ",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>% = Procent. Procent betekent per honderd.<br/>\n1% = <span class=\"math-tex\"><img alt=\"Formule\" src=\"https://mathjax-service.wikiwijs.nl/convert.svg?formula=MSBcb3ZlciAxMDAg\"/></span>= 0,01<br/>\n5% = <span class=\"math-tex\"><img alt=\"Formule\" src=\"https://mathjax-service.wikiwijs.nl/convert.svg?formula=NSBcb3ZlciAxMDA%3D\"/></span>= 0,05<br/>\n34% = <span class=\"math-tex\"><img alt=\"Formule\" src=\"https://mathjax-service.wikiwijs.nl/convert.svg?formula=MzQgXG92ZXIgMTAw\"/></span>= 0,34<br/>\nSommige percentages kom je vaak tegen. Het is belangrijk dat je die uit je hoofd kent:<br/>\n<br/>\nDe helft is <span class=\"math-tex\"><img alt=\"Formule\" src=\"https://mathjax-service.wikiwijs.nl/convert.svg?formula=MSBcb3ZlciAy\"/></span>= 50 : 100 = 50% = 0,5<br/>\nEen kwart is =<span class=\"math-tex\"><img alt=\"Formule\" src=\"https://mathjax-service.wikiwijs.nl/convert.svg?formula=MSBcb3ZlciA0IA%3D%3D\"/></span>= 25 : 100 = 25% = 0,25<br/>\nEen tiende is <span class=\"math-tex\"><img alt=\"Formule\" src=\"https://mathjax-service.wikiwijs.nl/convert.svg?formula=MSBcb3ZlciAxMA%3D%3D\"/></span>= 10 : 100 = 10% = 0,1</p>\n<p>Voorbeeld rekenen met procenten</p>\n<p>Voorbeeld percentage berekenen</p>\n<p>Voorbeeld rekenen met procentuele toename</p>\n<p>Voorbeeld rekenen met procentuele afname</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"124\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/xcezUzUjS5M\" width=\"173\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p>Wat zijn procenten?</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"124\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/MgcCjcfNf7E\" width=\"173\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p>Rekenen met procenten</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"124\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/A0eaPaNph08\" width=\"173\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p>Rekenen met %-toename</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"124\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/YgVzVw-4e8c\" width=\"173\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p>Rekenen met %-afname</p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"124\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/vKcbEM0dhSE\" width=\"173\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p>Berekenen percentage</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"124\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/cVxn8U_dsHA?rel=0\" width=\"173\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p>Van deel naar totaal</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
